message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with audio source separation and denoising, which falls under the domain of signal processing. Other likely categories could be cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper also deals with visual context, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper proposes a deep multi-instance multi-label learning framework, cs.MM (multimedia) as the paper deals with audio-visual object models, and cs.CL (computation and language) as the paper deals with audio processing.
